{"tid":2210753,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（牙醫/牙科生請入）隻牙咁樣斷係咪冇得救？「多圖」","createTime":"2020-09-20T15:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:58:43.000Z","uid":148233,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"aa376fd17b119ff3bcc50c6ff6ef0fa92eda5707","tid":2210753,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:52:00.000Z","msg":"小弟刷牙嗰陣feel到有隻牙有冤冤哋，仔細觀察咗一下發現左邊第一隻臼齒斷咗一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屋企附近牙醫診所因為疫情唔接case，所以上嚟問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好笑係我阿媽都係exac7ly嗰個牙同我一樣咁斷法，佢話我刷牙太大力刷斷咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"red\">Location：</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDJtfXo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDJtfXo.png&h=5722be24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rfp0RvK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfp0RvK.jpg&h=7b424612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GD1FRwo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGD1FRwo.png&h=e0faf973&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6PbeVX5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6PbeVX5.png&h=27fa0420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我同手指扯落少少牙肉就清楚啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zz0Rwt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zz0Rwt.png&h=81bd0d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平時有少少牙肉cover住所以唔影響嚼嘢，但飲凍嘢就會feel到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgKj64R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgKj64R.png&h=3c6b2aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後問下如果要整返預幾錢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想20歲頭就冇牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">感激不盡</span></span>"},{"pid":"710e50b161708c158b8024764a64cf9bc1dd7b9b","tid":2210753,"uid":30836,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"有啲牙醫診所仲會接case<br />\n搵下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248d193a438b81430746477fdb1131b053747b8c","tid":2210753,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"710e50b161708c158b8024764a64cf9bc1dd7b9b","tid":2210753,"uid":30836,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"有啲牙醫診所仲會接case<br />\n搵下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家個心囉囉攣瞓唔著"},{"pid":"0aa8e4eac7049eaa83246acc5eafb21207a0d460","tid":2210753,"uid":80902,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:57:03.000Z","msg":"利申唔係好識<br />\n<br />\n但就咁睇落去唔算斷呀, 崩左咋麻<br />\n補應該補得返<br />\n以前讀書我撞斷過隻牙, 真係無左一半, 都補得到, 過左十幾年都無事"},{"pid":"88c718673825ffea940246256b12f9d8ca385e50","tid":2210753,"uid":21481,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"喔 濕碎啦 唔係斷左<br />\n呢啲學名叫non carious cervical lesion<br />\n有機會係你刷牙 太大力刷蝕左 <br />\n都有機會係食酸野<br />\n<br />\n搵個肯睇既牙醫搞搞佢啦<br />\n通常會做返desensitization 或者補返"},{"pid":"59d75036d406e9177c9ad14ab3a53328554201c8","tid":2210753,"uid":233419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"唔係斷，係刷牙太大力刷蝕咗，如果敏感牙齒的話就咁補返就得"},{"pid":"301257e98a2febc50aea1f0afb0428e6fd132d10","tid":2210753,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0aa8e4eac7049eaa83246acc5eafb21207a0d460","tid":2210753,"uid":80902,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:57:03.000Z","msg":"利申唔係好識<br />\n<br />\n但就咁睇落去唔算斷呀, 崩左咋麻<br />\n補應該補得返<br />\n以前讀書我撞斷過隻牙, 真係無左一半, 都補得到, 過左十幾年都無事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />斷一半都得？咁堅"},{"pid":"f45fb7e8c50159189c9abab6b46e22b2fb544f49","tid":2210753,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88c718673825ffea940246256b12f9d8ca385e50","tid":2210753,"uid":21481,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"喔 濕碎啦 唔係斷左<br />\n呢啲學名叫non carious cervical lesion<br />\n有機會係你刷牙 太大力刷蝕左 <br />\n都有機會係食酸野<br />\n<br />\n搵個肯睇既牙醫搞搞佢啦<br />\n通常會做返desensitization 或者補返"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"多謝ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心都定一定"},{"pid":"9de642f608af0de3d54e4d13106ff5157e085531","tid":2210753,"uid":21481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f45fb7e8c50159189c9abab6b46e22b2fb544f49","tid":2210753,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88c718673825ffea940246256b12f9d8ca385e50","tid":2210753,"uid":21481,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"喔 濕碎啦 唔係斷左<br />\n呢啲學名叫non carious cervical lesion<br />\n有機會係你刷牙 太大力刷蝕左 <br />\n都有機會係食酸野<br />\n<br />\n搵個肯睇既牙醫搞搞佢啦<br />\n通常會做返desensitization 或者補返"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"多謝ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心都定一定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:01:50.000Z","msg":"唔客氣 緊張自己啲牙都係好事黎"},{"pid":"59d4125584848e76ff8ef2b5ba5526c06859a2d3","tid":2210753,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59d75036d406e9177c9ad14ab3a53328554201c8","tid":2210753,"uid":233419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"唔係斷，係刷牙太大力刷蝕咗，如果敏感牙齒的話就咁補返就得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"估唔到我老母都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝ching"},{"pid":"c9d