ces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:07:12.000Z","msg":"成日諗住大力就有用，跟住刷親都5min<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c76524e5631252768ed5debd9cf7659f4d35307","tid":2210753,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"應該冇得整, 要種牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都斷過 不過係中間斷開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2766f66cce7aaa03d45acda3aedbbd716e21190","tid":2210753,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"616ef4f7dc93ea672faba2e33d451f640fc06fb8","tid":2210753,"uid":221228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:06:44.000Z","msg":"dental abrasion（刷蝕）<br />\n刷牙唔好咁大力 可以補返佢 <br />\n但力度唔改既話個補粉會好易甩 幾年後可能又要補過<br />\n你前一隻都有 只係無咁深啫<br />\n通常刷蝕上下左右都有 有深有淺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:08:15.000Z","msg":"咁你都睇到仲有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係要搵多幾間診所問下接唔接case先"},{"pid":"9138c44a87bce61f784beee5fcf50d195e62ae88","tid":2210753,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c76524e5631252768ed5debd9cf7659f4d35307","tid":2210753,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"應該冇得整, 要種牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都斷過 不過係中間斷開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"唔好嚇我呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdad135465a898dbfb5fbcba967bdbe388370a9","tid":2210753,"uid":213142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"我都想幫屋企人問，佢種完牙一排，用電動刷牙刷到隻種牙冤冤地係咪正常"},{"pid":"62d65aafaa25039b04a1c54d364c074f197874cc","tid":2210753,"uid":40927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"係咪刷牙力度唔岩，主豬不如轉用電動牙刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f06349a9bd7cbd49b88bbb262d7443aa4497397","tid":2210753,"uid":317228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T17:27:17.000Z","msg":"呢d係abrasion(刷蝕)<br />\n<br />\n1)如冇傷到牙神經，可就咁補番<br />\n<br />\n2)如深到牙神經，就做杜牙根加支撐柱(post)<br />\n<br />\n唔好亂剝牙啦，你咁後生，而且真牙好珍寶，剝1隻少1隻，就算剝左種番都冇真牙咁好用"},{"pid":"c16d073a3b546f5bd90b6426688650a71dcb1023","tid":2210753,"uid":317228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T17:27:30.000Z","msg":"利申牙醫"},{"pid":"ec23209e34c9a83b47e0963fbb7004147b72b5a9","tid":2210753,"uid":153759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T18:17:21.000Z","msg":"唔係斷，上面有提到abrasion，唔排除有呢個可能，不過睇相更加似abfraction 即係由磨牙或者clenching 造成<br />\n<br />\n情況好常見，如果無牙齒過敏可以唔理佢，不過要做返個night guard 保護好啲牙<br />\n<br />\n利申：外國牙醫"},{"pid":"d622288009962b83422508e6781bda1ebca337e8","tid":2210753,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62d65aafaa25039b04a1c54d364c074f197874cc","tid":2210753,"uid":40927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"係咪刷牙力度唔岩，主豬不如轉用電動牙刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T00:49:01.000Z","msg":"我今朝已經好小心呵護佢哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇完醫生先決定轉唔轉牙刷，thx"},{"pid":"76e9f50a40d199db6bce95f58c9fce2bd4267e58","tid":2210753,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f06349a9bd7cbd49b88bbb262d7443aa4497397","tid":2210753,"uid":317228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T17:27:17.000Z","msg":"呢d係abrasion(刷蝕)<br />\n<br />\n1)如冇傷到牙神經，可就咁補番<br />\n<br />\n2)如深到牙神經，就做杜牙根加支撐柱(post)<br />\n<br />\n唔好亂剝牙啦，你咁後生，而且真牙好珍寶，剝1隻少1隻，就算剝左種番都冇真牙咁好用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T00:49:45.000Z","msg":"感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3945704663da63496b2bfd3afdf35598cc0f9672","tid":2210753,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec23209e34c9a83b47e0963fbb7004147b72b5a9","tid":2210753,"uid":153759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T18:17:21.000Z","msg":"唔係斷，上面有提到abrasion，唔排除有呢個可能，不過睇相更加似abfraction 即係由磨牙或者clenching 造成<br />\n<br />\n情況好常見，如果無牙齒過敏可以唔理佢，不過要做返個night guard 保護好啲牙<br />\n<br />\n利申：外國牙醫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T00:51:41.000Z","msg":"我諗唔係磨牙，由細到大都冇依個情況。都似係我刷牙太大力，因為女朋友有問過我點解刷牙咁大力，但係我唔覺大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}